By: Philalethes
---
The conjunction can take place only by means of the Moon or an imperfect body
and fire; and this Moon is the sap of the water of life, which is hidden in
Mercury, and is stirred up by fire; it is a spirit which enters the body, and
compels it to retain its soul.
